valworkbench.measures.internal.modelExplorer
Class ModelExplorer

java.lang.Object
  valworkbench.measures.Measure
      valworkbench.measures.internal.modelExplorer.ModelExplorer

public class ModelExplorer
extends Measure

The ModelExplorer class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing Model Explorer measure. This class takes in input a DataMatrix and an InputMeasure object. Values of mesaure are returned in a text file. The effect of computing such measure is basically to find a correct number of clusters with the given algorithm A and benchmark dataset D.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Raffaele Giancarlo, Filippo Utro, Davide Scaturro
